comment: Very tasty.  Sweet nose, strong taste with sweet finish.
Thick, honey/toffee, hint of spice and Vegemite type sourness to the sweetness. Very smooth for the cask strength.

Nose sweet, Apple, apricot, pear, cherry chocolate, 

Palate spices strong nuts 

Nice and powerful one.
It is good whisky for me. A

This is a great expression. PX comes out in the taste along with the oak. Fresh sweet fruit on the nose , vanilla on the nose and taste. Full body smooth with some bite in the middle then rounds and lingers in the end. Going to enjoy this bottle. I would definitely replace this when finished great value.
Very specific and interesting taste. Very smooth and drinkable
Perfect CS bottle with this age. But batch #3 is better

Nose: subdued caramel, marzipan, Christmas cake
